{
  "title": "Crunchy Uruguayan Butter Pecorino Stir-fry",
  "description": "This sick-day dish features a pescatarian-friendly blend of buttery and crunchy elements made with blanched pecorino cheese, perfect for quick meals or snacks.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
  "diet": [
